             was indicted for <rs id="t17830910-120-off627" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17830910-120-off627" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830910-120-off627" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17830910-120-cd628" type="crimeDate">8th day of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830910-120-off627 t17830910-120-cd628"></join> last, three looking-glasses in mahogany frames, value 5 s. twenty-four black lead pencils, value 7 s. 6 d. seven glasses for spectacles, value 6 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17830910-120-victim1244" type="victimName">
                           Richard 
                           Mountford
                        <interp inst="t17830910-120-victim1244" type="surname" value="Mountford"></interp>
